        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Unless you plan on having others research your spells for you, it's a good idea to dump your 5 points every level into that skill... researching spells to actually raise skill is a pain, and doing the concordance quests is even worse.  Only problem is it gets really expensive once you get past about 100 skill.</P><P>After doing this myself, my advice is find others to research for you... I wish I saved my points to dump into trade skills to raise all the appropriate ones to 21 off the bat.</P><P><img src="http://radio.cyberalert.com/eq/z-small.jpg" border=0><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
